                <p>Force majeure. Should for any reason outside of the control of the Company a days play or event be partly or wholly cancelled for any reason including bad weather, the Company will issue a credit voucher to the Client for the full value of any refund received from the venue or supplier. Individual companies may take out insurance coverage through their own broker.</p>

                <p>Liability. In making arrangements with third parties for carriage by air, hotel accommodation, transportation, restaurants or otherwise, the Company acts only as an agent of the Client and does so on the express condition that no liability of any kind howsoever caused shall attach to the Company in connection with or arising out of such arrangements.</p>

                <p>Licensing/Food & Liquor. When necessary the Company will adhere to the local Licensing Conditions for the provision of alcohol.</p>

