                <p>f. The undersigned warrants and represents that he or she is specifically authorized by the Client to execute Booking Contract and bind the Client to the obligations under Booking Contract. The Client acknowledges that the Company has relied on that representation. The Client agrees to abide by the rules, terms and conditions of the event facility. The Client cannot transfer or assign this Agreement without the written consent of the Company.</p>

                <p>g. The Company and any of its facilities and services provided under Booking Contract are totally independent of the event organisers and sponsors.</p>
